name: field-plot-and-accuracy-assessment-points-for-bents-old-fort-national-historic-site-vegetation-
notes: Accuracy Assessment, Observation and Plot Points. Plots within the park were identified and sampled in the summer of 2005. In the summer of 2006, randomly selected accuracy assessment plots were collected.
